She landed on the ground and transformed into bot mode.  She drew her 
gun and fired.  She fired at Deemos and Stronghold.  Her wings were 
leaking and her side had bullet holes in it.  She didn't care.  the 
pain could wait.  She had something to prove first.

She looked over and saw she was right near the cave entrance.
